A simple text file called pthread-stubs.pc will solve any configure requirements for this to be "installed."

Place the file in /boot/home/pkg/lib/pkgconfig:

Give it the following contents:

prefix=/boot/home/pkg
exec_prefix=${prefix}
libdir=/boot/home/pkg/lib

Name: pthread stubs
Description: Stubs missing from libc for standard pthread functions
Version: 0.3
Libs: 
